Ice Elementals
Ice Elementals have appeared in an abandoned part of a mine. The reason for their appearance has to be found, and in order to do so, you need samples of these elements.
#subobj 1
Enter the abandoned tunnels
The entrance to the abandoned mines is located in the center of the Mines zone, and is protected by a gate.
#subobj 2
Take the samples
In order to find the cause of the elementals' revelation, you need to destroy several of them and take their samples.